    directory: `<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2 2h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2Z"></path><path d="M7 12h10M7 16h7"></path></svg>`,
